COPY public.companies (id, country, description, industry, is_approved, logo, name, ot_policy, size, type, website) FROM stdin;
3	Đức	<h4 class="border-bottom-dashed ipb-4">Giới thiệu c&ocirc;ng ty</h4>\r\n<div class="paragraph ipt-4 text-break text-contain-hyperlink">WE REINVENT HOW BUSINESSES STAY, WORK AND PAY\r\n<p>HRS, a pioneer in business travel, aims to elevate every stay through innovative technology. With over 50 years of experience, their digital platform, driven by <strong>ProcureTech, TravelTech, </strong>and<strong> FinTech</strong>, transforms how companies and travelers <strong>Stay, Work, </strong>and <strong>Pay</strong>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>ProcureTech</strong> digitally revolutionizes lodging procurement, connecting corporations and suppliers in a cutting-edge ecosystem. This enables seamless efficiency and automation, surpassing travelers' expectations.</p>\r\n<p><strong>TravelTech</strong> redefines the online lodging experience, offering personalized content from selection to check-in, ensuring an unparalleled journey for corporate travelers.</p>\r\n<p>In <strong>FinTech</strong>, HRS introduces advancements like mobile banking and digital payments, turning corporate back offices into touchless lodging enablers, eliminating legacy cost barriers. The innovative 2-click book-to-pay feature streamlines interactions for travelers and hoteliers.</p>\r\n<p>Combining these technology propositions, HRS unlocks exponential catalyst effects. Their data-driven focus delivers value-added services and high-return network effects, creating substantial customer value.</p>\r\n<p>HRS's exponential growth since 1972 serves over 35% of the global Fortune 500 and leading hotel chains.</p>\r\n<p>Join HRS to shape the future of business travel, empowered by a culture of growth and setting new industry standards worldwide!</p>\r\n<p>More information at <a href="https://www.hrs.com/enterprise/">https://www.hrs.com/enterprise/</a></p>\r\n<h4 class="border-bottom-dashed ipb-4">Tại sao bạn sẽ y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch l&agrave;m việc tại đ&acirc;y?</h4>\r\n<div class="position-relative read-more-container show" data-controller="read-more" data-read-more-target="container">\r\n<div data-read-more-target="content">\r\n<ul class="paragraph ipt-4 text-break">\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700">Attractive salary package and valuable benefits</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700">Get the opportunity to access global L&amp;D programs</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700">Hybrid and flexible working environment</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700"><strong>Open and flat environment</strong>, highly appreciate your idea and constantly supporting your skill development.</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700"><strong>Innovative and international learning and development program</strong>, we dedicate to supporting employees&rsquo; growth and development of skills.</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700">Challenging products with&nbsp;<strong>onsite opportunities in Europe</strong> (Germany, Australia, Poland, etc.)</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700"><strong>Full salary and benefits</strong> as an official employee <strong>on probation</strong>.</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700"><strong>13th-month salary &amp; short-term incentives</strong>: we offer incentives as defined by the company&rsquo;s success in the previous year.</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700">15+ annual leaves per year.</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700">Full healthcare compliance.</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700">Premium healthcare for employees.</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700">Gifts for every special occasion.</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700">Supportive working conditions: Laptop, MS Surface Hub.</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700">Free and unlimited snacks, tea, coffee, and by-choice request.</li>\r\n<li class="ipy-1 fw-700">Premium company trip &amp; business traveling programs and other exciting activities.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>	Sản Phẩm Phần Mềm và Dịch Vụ Web	t	1740232941237-hrsgroup__logo.webp	HRS Group	Thêm lương OT	51-100 nhân viên	IT Product	https://www.hrs.com/enterprise/homepage/
5	Việt Nam	<h4 class="border-bottom-dashed ipb-4">Giới thiệu c&ocirc;ng ty</h4>\r\n<div class="paragraph ipt-4 text-break text-contain-hyperlink">MAKE YOU INVESTED @ DNSE\r\n<p>DNSE l&agrave; doanh nghiệp thuộc top những c&ocirc;ng ty chứng kho&aacute;n đầu ti&ecirc;n tại Việt Nam ti&ecirc;n phong ứng dụng c&ocirc;ng nghệ số hiện đại v&agrave;o sản phẩm t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh &ndash; chứng kho&aacute;n.</p>\r\n<p>TẦM NH&Igrave;N: đặt trọng t&acirc;m v&agrave;o việc kết nối nguồn vốn th&ocirc;ng qua c&ocirc;ng nghệ để dẫn dắt thị trường chứng kho&aacute;n số tại Việt Nam.</p>\r\n<p>SỨ MỆNH: &ldquo;ĐƠN GIẢN H&Oacute;A ĐẦU TƯ CHO NGƯỜI VIỆT&rdquo; th&ocirc;ng qua việc ứng dụng c&ocirc;ng nghệ hiện đại, tr&iacute; tuệ nh&acirc;n tạo v&agrave;o c&aacute;c sản phẩm &amp; dịch vụ, DNSE sẽ kh&ocirc;ng ngừng nỗ lực để kiến tạo hệ sinh th&aacute;i t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh &ndash; chứng kho&aacute;n số to&agrave;n diện v&agrave; tối ưu nhất, mang đến những quyết định đầu tư đơn giản - hiệu quả - thức thời hơn cho người Việt.</p>\r\n<p>GI&Aacute; TRỊ CỐT L&Otilde;I: lắng nghe thấu hiểu - t&ocirc;n trọng lời n&oacute;i - lu&ocirc;n l&agrave;m tốt hơn.</p>\r\n<h4 class="border-bottom-dashed ipb-4">Tại sao bạn sẽ y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch l&agrave;m việc tại đ&acirc;y?</h4>\r\n<div class="position-relative read-more-container show" data-controller="read-more" data-read-more-target="container">\r\n<div data-read-more-target="content">\r\n<div class="jd-photos ipt-2 ipb-6">\r\n<div class="slider-photos overflow-hidden">\r\n<div class="d-grid align-items-center igap-1 photo-grid" data-controller="jobs--jd-photos" data-jobs--jd-photos-show-headline-value="" data-jobs--jd-photos-url-value="/companies/dnse/jd_photos">\r\n<div class="col position-relative cursor-pointer"><picture data-action="click-&gt;jobs--jd-photos#open"> <source srcset="https://itviec.com/rails/active_storage/representations/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBOTlnT3c9PSIsImV4cCI6bnVsbCwicHVyIjoiYmxvYl9pZCJ9fQ==--