19	<section class="job-content imt-5 ipy-3 ipx-5 bg-it-white box-shadow-medium border-radius-large-md text-it-black" data-jobs--jd-scroll-target="jobContent">\r\n<div class="imy-3 paragraph">\r\n<h4>3 L&yacute; do để gia nhập c&ocirc;ng ty</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Very competitive remuneration package</li>\r\n<li>Build products for millions of users in Australia</li>\r\n<li>Hybrid and flexible working environment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imy-5 paragraph">\r\n<h4>M&ocirc; tả c&ocirc;ng việc</h4>\r\n<p><em><strong>By applying for the above position, you accept and agree that your personal data and any information stated in the attached curriculum vitae (CV) will be used and processed by ITViec and NAB Vietnam for recruitment purposes. The storage and processing of such information will comply with the applicable laws of Vietnam, and the policies and procedures of ITViec and NAB Vietnam regarding personal data, as amended from time to time.</strong></em></p>\r\n<p><strong>Your Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\r\n<p>Release Train Engineer's (RTE) major responsibilities are to manage and coordinate delivery in line with our Domain operating model, partnering with product owners and engineering as well as all technology teams required. RTEs communicate with stakeholders, plan delivery, resolve and escalate impediments, manage finances and risk and drive relentless improvement.&nbsp;<br>This role is also a servant leader and a coach for Agile Release Train (ART) and supports the implementation of new and better ways of working using Agile frameworks and methods&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br><strong>YOUR JOB RESPONSIBILITIES</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Devise a delivery plan and facilitate execution across diverse set of Agile development teams to ensure strategy and execution alignment&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Management of financials including obtaining estimates and resource plans to develop a consolidated forecast, then analysing any variances cross multiple&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Reporting and communication, including keeping key stakeholders informed of overall progress against the release commitments&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Provide coaching to help resolve issues across the relevant delivery squads&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Facilitate Agile release execution and planning events, including but not limited to progressive elaboration of breaking down large units of work into epics and features in collaboration of scrum masters and their squads&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Manage dependencies across squads and remove roadblocks to drive outcomes with product owners and business stakeholders&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Escalation points for dealing with issues, risks and removing bottlenecks/impediments&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Manage and optimise the flow of value and drive relentless improvement by assessing the agility level with a focus on improvement&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Coach leaders, teams and Scrum Masters in Agile practices and mindsets and promote a collaborative team environment&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Management of release readiness including SIT coordination, release approvals and high level deployment planning&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Contribute to the creation of a strong, capable and engaged team&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imy-5 paragraph">\r\n<h4>Y&ecirc;u cầu c&ocirc;ng việc</h4>\r\n<p><strong>Must have</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>At least 8 years project management experience relating to major IT projects.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Experience across Agile and adaptive delivery models and mindsets.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Track record of strong experience operating effectively and delivering consistent results in a large complex business.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Strong understanding of the software development lifecycle.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Good business awareness and commercial understanding.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br><strong>Nice-to-have</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Tertiary degree in finance, Banking and IT from a recognised institution is preferred.&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Agile Certification desirable.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imy-5 paragraph">\r\n<h4>Tại sao bạn sẽ y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch l&agrave;m việc tại đ&acirc;y</h4>\r\n<p><strong>1. Generous compensation and benefit package</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Attractive salary and benefits &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>20-day annual leave and 7-day sick leave, etc. &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>13th month salary and Annual Performance Bonus &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Premium healthcare for yourself and family members &nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>2. Exciting career and development opportunities </strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Large scale products with modern technologies in banking domain &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Clear roadmap for career advancement in both technical and leadership pathways &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Sponsored certificates in both IT and banking/finance &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Premium account on Udemy</li>\r\n<li>English learning with native teachers &nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>3. Professional and engaging working environment</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Hybrid working model and excellent work-life balance   &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Well-equipped &amp; modern Agile office with fully-stocked pantry  &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Annual company trip and events    <strong>A DIVERSE AND INCLUSIVE WORKPLACE WORKS BETTER FOR EVERYONE</strong>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>NAB is a place where colleagues of all genders, sexualities and ages, carers and colleagues with disability, and colleagues from all cultures, races and religions have the opportunity to thrive, connect and grow. <strong>If this excites you, let's have a chat over a cup of coffee!</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>	t	You'll love it	Senior Project Manager (Release Train Engineer)	2025-02-22 22:19:25.584	Hybrid	7
25	<section class="job-content imt-5 ipy-3 ipx-5 bg-it-white box-shadow-medium border-radius-large-md text-it-black" data-jobs--jd-scroll-target="jobContent">\r\n<div class="imy-3 paragraph">\r\n<h4>3 L&yacute; do để gia nhập c&ocirc;ng ty</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Very competitive remuneration package</li>\r\n<li>Build products for millions of users in Australia</li>\r\n<li>Hybrid and flexible working environment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imy-5 paragraph">\r\n<h4>M&ocirc; tả c&ocirc;ng việc</h4>\r\n<p><em><strong>By applying for the above position, you accept and agree that your personal data and any information stated in the attached curriculum vitae (CV) will be used and processed by ITViec and NAB Vietnam for recruitment purposes. The storage and processing of such information will comply with the applicable laws of Vietnam, and the policies and procedures of ITViec and NAB Vietnam regarding personal data, as amended from time to time.</strong></em></p>\r\n<p>Join our Cloud Consulting Services team, which is responsible for supporting the app teams in automating and streamlining the&nbsp;<strong>provisioning of Iaas, Paas and Database services</strong> across <strong>Azure, AWS</strong>. We embrace an <strong>Agile mindset</strong>, fostering a culture of collaboration, adaptability, and continuous improvement. As part of this role, you will work within Scrum practices, play a key part in <strong>risk, and change management</strong> processes to deliver high-quality cloud solutions efficiently and effectively. Our goal is providing a seamless multi-cloud experience, enabling the application teams to adopt cloud technologies efficiently while ensuring compliance with internal policies and industry standards</p>\r\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Cloud Infrastructure Development:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Design, develop, provision, and maintain cloud resources using Infrastructure as Code (IaC) tools (e.g., Terraform)</li>\r\n<li>Ensure automated infrastructure provisioning for Azure, AWS Environments complies with NAB standards and security controls.</li>\r\n<li>Performance regular patching, update, and security assessments on current project.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Database Services Management:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Provision and maintain cloud-based database services such as Azure SQL, PostgreSQL DB Flexi, AWS RDS&hellip;</li>\r\n<li>Perform regular security assessments and updates on database services</li>\r\n<li>Collaborate with database administrators to implement best practices for performance, security, and scalability</li>\r\n<li>Selecting appropriate tools for data migration and migrating data between database systems</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Agile and Scrum Practices:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Participate in Scrum ceremonies, including sprint planning, daily stand-ups, sprint reviews, and retrospectives</li>\r\n<li>Foster and Agile mindset within the team, encouraging continuous learning and iterative delivery</li>\r\n<li>Collaborate with the Scrum Master and Engineer Manager to ensure project timelines, goals and deliverables are met.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Risk and Chang management:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Identify, assess, and manage risks associated with cloud Infrastructure and database operations</li>\r\n<li>Proactively plan and implement changes to cloud environments, minimizing disruptions and ensuring business continuity</li>\r\n<li>Maintain documentation and communication channels to track and address change impacts effectively</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Security and Compliance:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Conduct Security reviews and vulnerability assessment for cloud resources, including database</li>\r\n<li>Ensure compliance with corporate policies and regulatory requirements for cloud-hosted resources and data</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Operational Excellence:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Monitor, Patch, and resolve defect in IaC environments</li>\r\n<li>Create documentation and processes for effective management of cloud and database resources</li>\r\n<li>Collaborate across teams to align cloud infrastructure with business goals and IT strategies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Innovation and Collaboration:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Keep pace with emerging cloud technologies and market trends</li>\r\n<li>Work closely with cross-functional stakeholders to integrate security, networking, and architecture requirements into the service delivery lifecycle</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imy-5 paragraph">\r\n<h4>Y&ecirc;u cầu c&ocirc;ng việc</h4>\r\n<p><strong>Must have:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>4+</strong>&nbsp;<strong>years</strong> - Hands-on experience with&nbsp;<strong>Azure</strong> and/or&nbsp;<strong>AWS resources</strong></li>\r\n<li>Proficiency in <strong>Terraform</strong> (Open-source and enterprise) for IaC development</li>\r\n<li>Experience with database platform like <strong>Azure SQL, PostgreSQL Flexi, AWS RDS,&nbsp;</strong>or similar services</li>\r\n<li>Familiarity with&nbsp;<strong>Linux operating systems and their administration</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Strong awareness</strong> of hardware systems, including servers, storage and networking, DNS devices / services.</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge of&nbsp;<strong>networking concepts</strong> such as VNET / VPC, Routing, firewalls, ExpressRoute, any subjects related to networking on cloud&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Familiarity with <strong>Agile practices and tool</strong>s (e.g., Rally, Confluence, Jira, or similar tools) and experience working in Scrum environments.</li>\r\n<li>Strong understanding of&nbsp;<strong>risk and change management principles</strong> and their application in cloud environments</li>\r\n<li>Familiarity with <strong>scripting and automation</strong> using tools like <strong>Git</strong>, <strong>Terraform</strong>, <strong>Bash</strong> <strong>Shell</strong>, <strong>PowerShell</strong>, Python</li>\r\n<li>Strong understanding of <strong>cloud security, compliance, and service management principles</strong></li>\r\n<li>Understanding the purpose and uses of encryption for database data at rest and data in transit</li>\r\n<li>Understanding about<strong> CI/CD Concept</strong></li>\r\n<li>A&nbsp;<strong>collaborative mindset</strong> to&nbsp;<strong>work with diverse teams</strong> and stakeholders effectively</li>\r\n<li>English proficiency at <strong>Upper Intermediate</strong>, ensuring clear communication in an international working environment.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Nice to have:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Understanding / Hands-on of&nbsp;<strong>Docker, Kubernetes</strong></li>\r\n<li>Hands on experience with <strong>CICD platform</strong> like Harness, Jenkins or similar platform.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imy-5 paragraph">\r\n<h4>Tại sao bạn sẽ y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch l&agrave;m việc tại đ&acirc;y</h4>\r\n<p><strong>1. Generous compensation and benefit package</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Attractive salary and benefits &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>20-day annual leave and 7-day sick leave, etc. &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>13th month salary and Annual Performance Bonus &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Premium healthcare for yourself and family members &nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>2. Exciting career and development opportunities </strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Large scale products with modern technologies in banking domain &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Clear roadmap for career advancement in both technical and leadership pathways &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Sponsored certificates in both IT and banking/finance &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Premium accounts on Udemy/A Cloud Guru/Coursera/LinkedIn, etc. &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>English learning with native teachers &nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>3. Professional and engaging working environment</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Hybrid working model and excellent work-life balance   &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Well-equipped &amp; modern Agile office with fully-stocked pantry  &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Annual company trip and events   &nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br><strong>A DIVERSE AND INCLUSIVE WORKPLACE WORKS BETTER FOR EVERYONE</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>NAB is a place where colleagues of all genders, sexualities and ages, carers and colleagues with disability, and colleagues from all cultures, races and religions have the opportunity to thrive, connect and grow.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br><strong>If this excites you, let's have a chat over a cup of coffee!</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>	t	You'll love it	Senior Cloud Engineer - HCM	2025-02-22 22:35:55.662	Hybrid	7
13	<section class="job-content imt-5 ipy-3 ipx-5 bg-it-white box-shadow-medium border-radius-large-md text-it-black" data-jobs--jd-scroll-target="jobContent">\r\n<div class="imy-3 paragraph">\r\n<h4>3 L&yacute; do để gia nhập c&ocirc;ng ty</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Attractive salary package and valuable benefits</li>\r\n<li>Get the opportunity to access global L&amp;D programs</li>\r\n<li>Hybrid and flexible working environment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imy-5 paragraph">\r\n<h4>M&ocirc; tả c&ocirc;ng việc</h4>\r\n<p>We are looking for a <strong>Senior Azure cloud infrastructure and DevOps Engineer</strong> (all genders) who loves building top-notch SAAS products while creating infrastructure, tools, templates, and many more that enable colleagues to ship value at unprecedented speed to customers. You will work on one of our core SAAS systems utilizing state-of-the-art technology</p>\r\n<p><strong>CHALLENGE</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Managing&nbsp;the&nbsp;Azure&nbsp;cloud&nbsp;and&nbsp;system:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Managing the&nbsp;cloud&nbsp;services&nbsp;such&nbsp;as&nbsp;VMs,&nbsp;databases,&nbsp;storages,&nbsp;and&nbsp;other&nbsp;cloud&nbsp;services</li>\r\n<li>Ensuring the&nbsp;performance, availability, scalability, and&nbsp;security</li>\r\n<li>Managing&nbsp;the&nbsp;backup&nbsp;and&nbsp;disaster&nbsp;recovery solutions</li>\r\n<li>Optimizing the&nbsp;data&nbsp;center&nbsp;cost</li>\r\n<li>Keeping&nbsp;up-to-date&nbsp;cloud&nbsp;technology&nbsp;and&nbsp;improving&nbsp;the&nbsp;infrastructure</li>\r\n<li>Managing access to cloud services and build automated policies around this&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Maintaining and developing the DevOps:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Maintaining and developing CI/CD pipelines, automated deployment processes, and Infrastructure as Code (IaC)</li>\r\n<li>Maintaining and developing IaC scripts, templates, and configuration management tools</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Managing the system security:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Maintaining and developing the policies, procedures, and controls to ensure compliance with ISO 27001, PCI DSS, SOC 1&amp;2</li>\r\n<li>Monitoring and analyzing the security logs, events, and alerts to ensure system security</li>\r\n<li>Preparing and participating in the ISMS internal and external audits</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Managing the team:&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Managing and leading a team of 3-5 members to achieve the team's goals and objectives</li>\r\n<li>Collaborating and aligning with the group - HRS Corporate IT - on the vision, strategy and roadmap&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imy-5 paragraph">\r\n<h4>Y&ecirc;u cầu c&ocirc;ng việc</h4>\r\n<p><strong>FOR THIS EXCITING MISSION YOU ARE EQUIPPED WITH...</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Comprehensive&nbsp;knowledge experience of&nbsp;cloud computing models (IaaS,&nbsp;PaaS, SaaS),&nbsp;virtualization,&nbsp;server&nbsp;and&nbsp;storage&nbsp;management,&nbsp;networking,&nbsp;and&nbsp;security&nbsp;on&nbsp;cloud&nbsp;such&nbsp;as&nbsp;<strong>Azure</strong>&nbsp;(preferable)</li>\r\n<li>Experience with&nbsp;operating&nbsp;systems&nbsp;such&nbsp;as&nbsp;<strong>Linux&nbsp;and&nbsp;Windows&nbsp;Server</strong>,&nbsp;especially&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;cloud&nbsp;environment</li>\r\n<li>Proficiency&nbsp;in&nbsp;automation&nbsp;and&nbsp;scripting&nbsp;languages&nbsp;such&nbsp;as&nbsp;PowerShell,&nbsp;Python,&nbsp;Bash,&nbsp;and&nbsp;tools&nbsp;like&nbsp;Ansible,&nbsp;Terraform</li>\r\n<li>Good&nbsp;knowledge of network architecture,&nbsp;protocols, and security, especially cloud-based&nbsp;services&nbsp;like&nbsp;Virtual&nbsp;PrivateClouds,&nbsp;Load&nbsp;Balancers</li>\r\n<li>Good&nbsp;knowledge&nbsp;and&nbsp;experience&nbsp;of&nbsp;CI/CD&nbsp;automated&nbsp;process,&nbsp;tools&nbsp;and&nbsp;framework&nbsp;such&nbsp;as&nbsp;Jenkins, GitLab, Travis CI</li>\r\n<li>Experience with&nbsp;cloud-based&nbsp;monitoring and troubleshooting&nbsp;tools like Azure Monitor, PRTG,&nbsp;Prometheus, Grafana...</li>\r\n<li>Understanding&nbsp;of&nbsp;security&nbsp;principles,&nbsp;protocols, practices&nbsp;and&nbsp;framework&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;cloud&nbsp;such&nbsp;as&nbsp;Identity and&nbsp;Access&nbsp;Management&nbsp;(IAM),&nbsp;data&nbsp;encryption&nbsp;and&nbsp;protection,&nbsp;OWAPS,&nbsp;SANS,&nbsp;NIST</li>\r\n<li>Excellent&nbsp;communication and&nbsp;collaboration&nbsp;skills&nbsp;while&nbsp;working with&nbsp;development&nbsp;team,&nbsp;IT&nbsp;teams,&nbsp;and&nbsp;other&nbsp;stakeholders in&nbsp;both&nbsp;English and&nbsp;Vietnamese</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="imy-5 paragraph">\r\n<h4>Tại sao bạn sẽ y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch l&agrave;m việc tại đ&acirc;y</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Full salary and benefits</strong> as an official employee <strong>on probation</strong>.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Hybrid working</strong> model.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Open and flat environment</strong>, highly appreciate your idea and constantly supporting your skill development.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Innovative and international learning and development program</strong>, we dedicate to supporting employees&rsquo; growth and development of skills.</li>\r\n<li>Challenging products with <strong>onsite opportunities in Europe</strong> (Germany, Australia, Poland, etc.).</li>\r\n<li><strong>13th-month salary &amp; short-term incentives</strong>: we offer incentives as defined by the company&rsquo;s success in the previous year.</li>\r\n<li>15+ annual leaves per year.</li>\r\n<li>Full healthcare compliance.</li>\r\n<li>Premium healthcare for employees.</li>\r\n<li>Gifts for every special occasion.</li>\r\n<li>Supportive working conditions: Laptop, MS Surface Hub.</li>\r\n<li>Free and unlimited snacks, tea, coffee, and by-choice request.</li>\r\n<li>Premium company trip &amp; business traveling programs and other exciting activities.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Note: Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. Thanks for your interest!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>	t	2,000 - 3,000 USD	Senior Azure Cloud 